1D Convolution in FFT Block
We propose to replace the original fully connected layer ( adopted in Transformer ) with 1D convolution in FFT block , as described in Section 3.1 .

results in.from sentence: As shown in , replacing 1D convolution with fully connected layer results in - 0.113 CMOS , which demonstrates the effectiveness of 1D convolution .
